title: The Best of The Dan Patrick Show
itunes:title: The Best of The Dan Patrick Show
description:
On today's Dan Patrick Show, DP recaps Week 8 in the NFL; who's his MVP at this point in the season? Ross Tucker discusses the Cowboys' playoff chances without Ezekiel Elliot. Fritzy's Halloween Sports Name bomb. And the guys preview their setup for Trick or Treaters tonight. 

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
